snippet.title: Wild 9 (PS1) Gameplay
snippet.description:
From the makers of Earthworm Jim comes Wild 9 on Playstyation.  I'm not too familiar with the game, I remember I rented it once back in the day. I was at a local gamestore today and picked it up for $2.99 along with Tenchu and Tenchu 2. 

I do not plan on doing a playthrough of this game, I'll just do the final battle and ending IF i can get that far, heh.
